From f111da309c22b563704ed3460c241f2181136270 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ji Luo <ji.luo@nxp.com>
Date: Tue, 23 Dec 2025 14:43:43 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] MATTER-3820-1 Enable trusty drivers for k6.18

Add trusty drivers support for matter k6.18. This commit
is a collection of below commits:
	MA-13966 Route Trusty OS log to Linux end
	MA-20082-1 ANDROID: trusty-log: enlarge buffer size for old trusty api version
	MA-17372-1 trusty: remove trusty-log buffer when shutdown
	MA-24298 allow memory lend for old api level
	GKI: Adapt to upstream dma-buf locking changes
	trusty: Defer the clearing of signaled until FFA_RUN
	ANDROID: trusty: fix warnings from missing-prototypes
	trusty-virtio: Use hrtimer_setup on newer kernels
	ANDROID: trusty: Get rid of 'remove_new' relic from platform driver struct
	ANDROID: trusty-ipc: Convert DMA_BUF symbol namespace to string literal
	trusty-ffa: Enqueue NOP on SRI
	trusty-ipc: fix return value on error path
	trusty-ffa-transport: reference the FF-A bus statically
	trusty-virtio: Add module parameter for default polling period
	include: smcall: Add TRUSTY_FFA_MSG_IS_IDLE
	trusty-virtio: Add periodic timer for check_vqs
	trusty-ffa: Remove children on shutdown
	trusty-populate: Add new module that populates devices
	ANDROID: trusty-ffa: Enable FFA transport
	trusty-test: Add secure timer to FP test
	ANDROID: trusty: Add trusty-ffa driver
	ANDROID: trusty: Separate out SMC based transport
	ANDROID: trusty-sched-share: Add IDLE shadow priority
	trusty: Cast SMC numbers and errors to 32-bit
	trusty-virtio: Add release function to virtio devices
	trusty-ipc: Fix some shutdown bugs
	trusty: Ignore NOT_SUPPORTED error for FFA_MEM_SHARE init
	trusty: Add trusty_get_state getter with extra checks
	trusty-test: Add fpsimd tests
	trusty: Remove some debug statements
	trusty: Added NOP DMA functions to trusty-virtio
	ANDROID: trusty-test: Fix parsing of arguments
	Fix headers include variable
	Add include paths to Makefile
	ANDROID: trusty_log: comply with platform_driver::remove() returning void (v6.11 compat)
	ANDROID: trusty: comply with platform_driver::remove() returning void (v6.11 compat) round 2
	ANDROID: trusty: Support pseudo-nmi mode.
	ANDROID: trusty: comply with platform_driver::remove() returning void (v6.11 compatibility)
	ANDROID: trusty: Add SECURE_OR_SHARE transfer
	ANDROID: trusty: Fix changes to find_vqs
	ANDROID: trusty: Fix build errors from v6.10 merge
	ANDROID: trusty: Rename transfer memory to lend
	Fix class_create wrapper macro on pre-6.4 kernels
	Trusty driver compat 6.7 shrinker interface
	Trusty driver compat 6.4 class_create()
	Trusty driver compat 6.0 register_shrinker()
	Trusty driver compat 5.16 MODULE_IMPORT_NS
	Trusty driver compat 5.14 panic_notifier
	trusty: add the TRUSTY virtio id to trusty-ipc.c
	Trusty driver toolchain compatibility
	ANDROID: Eliminate vqueue map/unmap for each msg
	ANDROID: trusty: Make Trusty driver page size agnostic
	ANDROID: trusty-ipc: correct data_source flag of struct iov_iter in filp_send_ioctl()
	ANDROID: trusty: fix use-after-free
	ANDROID: trusty: Make trusty-irq part of trusty-core module.
	ANDROID: Delay sharing sched memory with Trusty
	ANDROID: trusty: Call kthread_set_per_cpu
	ANDROID: trusty-log: fix potential use-after-free
	ANDROID: trusty: park threads when cpu is offline
	ANDROID: trusty: Print error message if trusty_nop_thread runs on wrong cpu
	ANDROID: improve trusty kthread priority
	ANDROID: escalate kthread nice for Trusty
	ANDROID: Use kthread for trusty work instead of wq
	ANDROID: trusty: Create API for sharing trusty info
	ANDROID: trusty: Add trace points
	ANDROID: trusty: Use high priority check WQ and regular nop WQ
	ANDROID: trusty-log: fix poll check for data availability.
	ANDROID: trusty: add a toggle for running trusty work in higher priority
	ANDROID: trusty-log: Optionally copy Trusty log to kernel log
	ANDROID: trusty-log: make rate limit configurable
	ANDROID: trusty: Enforce only TRUSTY_SEND_SECURE can send secure memory
	ANDROID: trusty-ipc: Allow registering multiple handles
	ANDROID: trusty: Support setting trusty_shared_mem_id_t
	ANDROID: trusty-log: rework buffer allocation
	ANDROID: trusty-ipc: Fix lock protection of shared_handles
	ANDROID: trusty-log: support poll()
	ANDROID: trusty-irq: enqueue work in trusty_irq_cpu_up
	ANDROID: trusty: Add config TRUSTY_CRASH_IS_PANIC
	ANDROID: trusty-ipc: Fix crash when running out of txbuffers
	ANDROID: trusty: Allow TRUSTY_LEND of buffers
	ANDROID: trusty-virtio: remove unnecessary include of dma-mapping.h
	ANDROID: trusty-log: Complement logging sink with unthrottled virtual file
	ANDROID: trusty-log: Refactor logging state to support concurrent sinks
	ANDROID: trusty-log: Sanitize u32 overflow of the log ring buffer write index
	ANDROID: trusty-log: On trusty panic, unthrottle sink to the kernel log
	ANDROID: trusty-log: Update trusty log buffer size to hold a complete Trusty crash logs
	ANDROID: trusty: Support setting FF-A Tag
	ANDROID: trusty-ipc: Switch from memfd to dma_buf
	ANDROID: trusty-irq: specify IPIs in new way
	ANDROID: trusty: Add trusty-test driver
	ANDROID: trusty: Add trusty-ipc driver
	ANDROID: trusty: Add trusty-virtio driver
	ANDROID: trusty: Add trusty-log driver
	ANDROID: trusty: Add trusty-irq driver
	ANDROID: trusty: Add trusty-core driver

